1
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,360
Did you pause the live stream?

2
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:34,800
I have to go back and make up for my classes.

3
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,000
When you come back,

4
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,660
we can continue our business.

5
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:40,560
I promise I will be back as soon as possible.

6
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:42,820
Then you must take good care of yourself.

7
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:47,920
Alright, I'm off.

8
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:00,680
November 3, 2016.

9
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:03,320
An Yufan can finally go home.

10
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:06,050
I wonder if after he returned to Aners,

11
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,920
everything went smoothly.

12
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,120
Mr. An, we have arrived.

13
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,120
What the book says here is

14
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:18,080
spiritual products reflecting market forms.

15
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,520
So what is this section actually about?

16
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,720
First, we need to look at the definition.

17
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,800
November 5th.

18
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:27,000
I feel like Yufan has been very busy since he went back.

19
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,000
But we still agreed

20
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,760
to have a call on time every day.

21
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,200
Zixi.

22
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,240
Are you done with work?

23
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:33,840
Yes.

24
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,800
That's good.

25
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,440
By the way.

26
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,460
Did you see the message I sent you?

27
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,080
Those are some gifts I picked out.

28
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:39,800
Yeah, I know.

29
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,920
Most importantly, you need to drink more hot water.

30
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:44,180
You caught a cold right after going back.

31
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,840
Sorry, the meeting ran overtime today.

32
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,720
I know.

33
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,880
I'll go back after finishing this project.

34
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,199
Really?

35
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:14,200
Yufan, are you done with the meeting?

36
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:28,760
That's all for today's class.

37
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:31,280
The time for the final exam has been set.

38
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,840
If you still don't know it,

39
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,360
check the school intranet yourself.

40
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,360
Class dismissed.

41
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,920
Tomorrow...

42
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,280
will he come back?

43
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,650
Were you staring at me in the hallway just now?

44
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,160
Zixi.

45
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,060
You should be fine with this exam, right?

46
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,329
No need for tutoring this time.

47
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:20,540
That's true. You haven't live-streamed in a long time.

48
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,240
Oh, right.

49
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,880
Where is your live-streaming equipment?

50
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,800
Let me help you set it up in the dorm.

51
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,200
I'm not doing it anymore.

52
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,960
Your account has so many followers.

53
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,480
It would be a pity to stop.

54
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,040
Live-streaming isn't a one-person job.

55
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,480
I can help you.

56
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,040
I happen to have a large batch of goods.

57
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,800
We can split the profits 50-50.

58
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,880
I'm not live-streaming lately.

59
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,340
We'll talk about it later.

60
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,680
Zixi, are you asleep?

61
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,159
Sorry for waking you up.

62
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,440
What are you looking for?

63
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,240
My diary is missing.

64
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,120
Missing?

65
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,930
Did you leave it somewhere?

66
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,160
I usually carry it with me.

67
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,160
Isn't today An Yufan's birthday?

68
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,570
Aren't you going to prepare for it?

69
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,880
How do you know?

70
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,760
I...

71
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,640
I heard it from someone in the student council.

72
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,100
From the student council?

73
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,240
I think so.

74
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,960
What surprise did he prepare for you today?

75
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,960
Surprise?

76
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:30,240
Hasn't he been really busy with work lately?

77
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,280
Yufan, are you back?

78
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,730
You're here.

79
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,040
Right here.

80
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,440
So it's a prop for my birthday.

81
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,640
Zixi.

82
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,040
How are you doing?

83
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,960
Who are you?

84
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,560
How could you just walk into the ward?

85
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,620
I'm her boyfriend.

86
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,880
Even a boyfriend is not allowed.

87
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:00,320
Get out.

88
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,360
No visiting without the guardian's permission.

89
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,200
No, Doctor.

90
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,360
What's wrong with her?

91
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,840
The patient has a relapse of brain trauma.

92
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,100
She needs to rest until fully recovered.

93
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,080
Get out.

94
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,620
Don't provoke the patient for no reason.

95
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:43,440
Zixi.

96
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,040
Casting Director: Xi Chongjing

97
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,920
Props Assistant: Li Kunxiao

98
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,880
Grip Truck: Yi Mingle

99
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,840
Yitong.
